title: Migrants scale U.S.-Mexico border wall during protest
text:
Migrants scale U.S.-Mexico border wall during protest 3:04am IST - 00:35
A handful of Central American migrants scaled the border fence dividing the U.S. and Mexico on Sunday (April 29) during a demonstration in support of the migrants. Rough Cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
